                <h2>Where We've Come From</h2>
                <p>
                    Founded in 2008, The Fancy Computer Store has grown from a small PC and mobile repair business to one of the largest and fastest growing value-added-resellers of technology products in Canada. We service customers of all sizes and types from Vancouver to Halifax and everywhere in between.
                        <br />
                    Our 17 retail locations in southern British Columbia have been providing exceptional products and services to our communities for the better part of 10 years. We are now proud to sell products both in-store and online and are able to continue to provide value to our customers all across this great country of ours.
                        <br />
                    FCS has built its reputation on honesty, integrity, and clarity of service, and we’re not changing that anytime soon.
                        <br />
                </p>
